{"tid":1052635,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「神的美少女」黑木光高中畢業了！為拍性感寫真慘遭美少女戰士換角","createTime":"2019-03-08T12:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T12:40:12.000Z","uid":9573,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a1719ab561d6952f1bc21e9d42d6b23b11d57e1a","tid":1052635,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"「神的美少女」日本混血女模黑木光，14歲時被星探發掘，因為天使外表魔鬼身材，讓她在日本大受歡迎。現在已經18歲的她，將在月底發行寫真集，像大家宣告她「畢業了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/08/1815316-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F08%2F1815316-XXL.jpg&h=2a96c9b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲被譽為「神的美少女」的日本混血女模黑木光。<br />\n<br />\n黑木光在2016年獲選舞台劇《美少女戰士》中「水星仙子」的角色，但被粉絲告發，她國三時當寫真偶像，拍了許多露出乳溝、開腿等太過性感的寫真，因此不適合演出「水星仙子」，黑木光便主動辭演該劇。這件事卻讓黑木光意外爆紅，更被媒體冠上「神的美少女」稱號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3422/d3422330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3422%2Fd3422330.jpg&h=155cdead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.cinra.net/uploads/img/news/2018/20181113-arimurakasumi_full.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinra.net%2Fuploads%2Fimg%2Fnews%2F2018%2F20181113-arimurakasumi_full.jpg&h=2e0c1fa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲被譽為「神的美少女」的日本混血女模黑木光。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，黑木光受訪時曾說過，自己從國中開始就邊讀書邊工作，現在她即將高中畢業，覺得以後和同學們見面的時間會變少，因此感到十分寂寞傷心。她表示，會好好珍惜最後的高中時光。而畢業之後她將繼續朝演員、模特兒之路發展，她也期待自己的演藝之路能夠順遂。<br />\n<br />\n▼圖為黑木光<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/08/1815343-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F08%2F1815343-XXL.jpg&h=af1a0db1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼圖為黑木光<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/08/1815345-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F08%2F1815345-XXL.jpg&h=4027a851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼圖為朱千雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kw9CLuu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkw9CLuu.jpg&h=4df4f7fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e98d29dd4a06aa5d05c3dca7c8970a13c7287cd9","tid":1052635,"uid":815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T12:40:12.000Z","msg":"千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}